OL,3,CParalympian Dame Sarah Storey 'so
OL,4,Cproud' as she calls time on
OL,5,Cillustrious career
OL,7,FDame Sarah Storey has announced her
OL,8,Fretirement from competitive sport,
OL,9,Fending a career which saw her become
OL,10,FGreat Britain's most successful
OL,11,FParalympian.
OL,13,FStorey, 48, won a British record 19
OL,14,FParalympic gold medals across swimming
OL,15,Fand cycling, but has opted to step
OL,16,Faway from competition two years ahead
OL,17,Fof what could have been her 10th
OL,18,FParalympic Games in Los Angeles.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
