OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783684141
OL,3,CParalympian Dame Sarah Storey 'so
OL,4,Cproud' as she calls time on
OL,5,Cillustrious career
OL,7,F"I am so privileged to have spent 35
OL,8,Fyears as an international athlete,"
OL,9,Fthe Cheshire athlete said.
OL,11,F"I genuinely pinch myself that my
OL,12,Fchildhood dream of being an athlete
OL,13,Ffor as long as I possibly could has
OL,14,Fled to nine Paralympic Games and
OL,15,Fopportunities across so many sporting
OL,16,Fevents.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@cO]sD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783684141
OL,3,CParalympian Dame Sarah Storey 'so
OL,4,Cproud' as she calls time on
OL,5,Cillustrious career
OL,7,F"This has included women's and Para
OL,8,Fsport alike, and I feel so proud to
OL,9,Fhave contributed ` alongside so many
OL,10,Fincredible people ` to the progress
OL,11,Fwe've all witnessed and enjoyed in
OL,12,Fthat time."
OL,14,FStorey made her Paralympic debut as a
OL,15,Fswimmer at the Barcelona Games in
OL,16,F1992, taking time off school to
OL,17,Fcompete at the age of just 14. She won
OL,18,Ftwo gold medals there and three more
OL,19,Fin Atlanta four years later.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783684141
OL,3,CParalympian Dame Sarah Storey 'so
OL,4,Cproud' as she calls time on
OL,5,Cillustrious career
OL,7,FShe won four silver medals and a
OL,8,Fbronze across the Sydney and Athens
OL,9,FGames before switching to cycling
OL,10,Fahead of Beijing 2008.
OL,12,FShe went on to win another 14
OL,13,FParalympic gold medals ` nine in road
OL,14,Fcycling and another five in the
OL,15,Fvelodrome.
OL,17,FFour of her titles came in front of
OL,18,Fhome crowds in London, and she retires
OL,19,Fas a reigning Paralympic champion
OL,20,Fafter a double success in Paris two
OL,21,Fyears ago.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783684141
OL,3,CParalympian Dame Sarah Storey 'so
OL,4,Cproud' as she calls time on
OL,5,Cillustrious career
OL,7,F"Physically, I fully believe that I
OL,8,Fcould be on that start line in Los
OL,9,FAngeles, confident of defending my two
OL,10,Ftitles from Paris," Storey added.
OL,12,F"However, I believe I can now be a
OL,13,Fmore positive influence leveraging new
OL,14,Froles and opportunities that allow me
OL,15,Fto fight for Para sport, and the
OL,16,Fcoverage that it deserves."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@SO]tD@AOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783684141
OL,3,CParalympian Dame Sarah Storey 'so
OL,4,Cproud' as she calls time on
OL,5,Cillustrious career
OL,7,FHer announcement comes ahead of this
OL,8,Fsummer's Commonwealth Games in
OL,9,FGlasgow, where the Para sport schedule
OL,10,Fhas been integrated into the
OL,11,Fcompetition schedule.
OL,13,FHowever, Storey feels more needs to be
OL,14,Fdone to keep developing Para sport.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783684141
OL,3,CParalympian Dame Sarah Storey 'so
OL,4,Cproud' as she calls time on
OL,5,Cillustrious career
OL,7,F"There's also no doubt in my mind
OL,8,Fthat, within Para sport, we have
OL,9,Fstalled somewhat since London 2012,
OL,10,Fand the years between each Games
OL,11,Fhaven't been utilised well enough to
OL,12,Fcreate the momentum that I and others
OL,13,Fhoped to see," she added.
OL,15,F"I see this as a critical stage; there
OL,16,Fare many areas of Para sport that
OL,17,Fstill need attention, and that is
OL,18,Fsomething that has played a big part
OL,19,Fin my decision.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@NO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783684141
OL,3,CParalympian Dame Sarah Storey 'so
OL,4,Cproud' as she calls time on
OL,5,Cillustrious career
OL,7,F"I fully believe that I can have a
OL,8,Fgreater impact off my bike, rather
OL,9,Fthan chasing a 10th Games and possibly
OL,10,Ffurther titles.
OL,12,F"I'm excited to be part of a future
OL,13,Fwhere we inject the momentum that is
OL,14,Fneeded to ensure the future is bright
OL,15,Ffor all Para athletes."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
